             was indicted for <rs id="t17840707-79-off398" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17840707-79-off398" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840707-79-off398" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17840707-79-cd399" type="crimeDate">16th day of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840707-79-off398 t17840707-79-cd399"></join> last, one gelding, price ten pounds
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17840707-79-victim791" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Hitchman
                  <interp inst="t17840707-79-victim791" type="surname" value="Hitchman"></interp>
